{"type": "article", "id": 3599, "title": "The Earth 2014 Harris Tweed 合作系列包袋", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-17T08:01:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232628R5YE8zKOhPkBNuUd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t韩国包袋品牌 The Earth 每年冬天都会携手英国羊毛物料制造商 Harris Tweed 推出当季的 Harris Tweed 羊毛材质制成的包袋系列。最近，双方公布了今年的「The Earth 2014 Harris Tweed」合作系列，包含一款斜挎包、一款双肩背包、一款手提包、一款单肩包以及相机背带。今年的联名系列继续选用优质的羊毛料材质，在设计上运用了经典的格纹元素和皮革材质的点缀。定价 39000－198000 韩元不等，<a href=\"http://theearthshop.co.kr/product/list.html?cate_no=77\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232625r4HfKsdk0XDU59g2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232626JpF0Y27la4yxRwsg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232626aDvmg5kGrcI2CpVt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232627E3KNVRhkM89orlqP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232627iBdr4AFaMmzLkYwn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}